article_id:276,category_name:News,title_name:Monthly Purchase Limits Reset!,image_path:,message:<div>We have reset the purchase limit on items that can only be purchased once per month in the Shop!</div><div>Players who already purchased these last month may now purchase them once again.</div><div><br></div><div>Here are the items which can only be purchased once per month:</div><div><br></div><div>■Unbind Pack (Mana Circles)</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/cb0a7f3c1328157fd52ffb03bd389095.png"></div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items to help you unlock mana nodes and unbind mana circles.</div><div>Recommended to upgrade your adventurers!</div><div><br></div><div>■Unbind Pack (Weapons)</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/6b83fa547ae5aaf8b4be91c4c871ddfb.png"></div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items to help you unbind 5★ weapons.</div><div>Recommended to boost your arsenal!</div><div><br></div><div>■Unbind Pack (Wyrmprints)</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/d1703979bbef846beb6fd69d942f529f.png"></div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items to help you unbind 5★ wyrmprints.</div><div>Recommended to upgrade your wyrmprints!</div><div><br></div><div>■Unbind Pack (Dragons)</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9a828ff4d0b4aeaea9ee6c5d59876569.png"></div><div>This pack contains diamantium and items to help you unbind 5★ dragons.</div><div>Recommended to strengthen your dragons!</div><div><br></div><div>For more details on these packs&#39; contents and prices, please check the &quot;This Month&quot; tab of the &quot;Upgrade Essentials&quot; menu in the Shop.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1551445200,update_time1551445339